### Why this is safe/minimal
- The rules are confined to `.hero`/`.hero-title` and to obvious control wrappers (`#blog-controls`, `.blog-controls`, `.blog-filters`). If **`blog.css` is only referenced by your blog listing and post pages**, these overrides won’t touch the homepage.
