Why this works:
- Using **`ch`** keeps line length readable (≈ characters per line) while naturally increasing **side margins** as the viewport grows.
- Responsive `padding-inline` adds a bit more breathing room without affecting mobile.
- No HTML changes needed; it only targets `.post` (present on `blog-post.html`), so your listing grid stays untouched.

